, figs. 10a-b-c; 
<figureCitation id="1348AC89FFC4FFFE089FFB27FDA308C6" box="[460,518,1186,1210]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="16.[151,186,1282,1304]" captionTargetBox="[149,1433,259,1260]" captionTargetId="figure-361@16.[148,1433,259,1265]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="Fig. 7: A-C: Hildaites planiventris n. sp., holotype MSA61, shell draw (x1), whorl section (x1) and suture (x3). D-E: Hildaites bisulcatus n. sp., holotype MSA351, whorl section (x1) and suture (x3). F-G: Hildaites calamantis n. sp., holotype MSA85, whorl section (x1) and suture (x2)." pageId="17" pageNumber="101">Fig.7</figureCitation>
